+# Coordination Log
+
+Use this file to share decisions, status updates, and context with other agents.
+Write your updates below. There is no enforced format — use whatever structure helps.
+
+---
+
+## Analytics Dashboard API (completed)
+
+**What was done:**
+- Created `src/models/analytics.ts` with three interfaces: `AnalyticsSummary`, `UserAnalytics`, `TrendPoint`
+- Created `src/services/analytics.service.ts` with `AnalyticsService` class using constructor DI (UserRepository, OrderRepository)
+  - `getSummary()` — aggregates totalUsers, totalOrders, revenue, activeUsers (users with at least one order)
+  - `getUserAnalytics(userId)` — per-user order count, total spent, last active date
+  - `getTrends(metric, startDate, endDate)` — groups orders by day, supports 'orders' and 'revenue' metrics
+- Created `tests/services/analytics.service.test.ts` with 13 tests covering all methods, edge cases, and error paths
+
+**Key decisions:**
+- `activeUsers` defined as users who have at least one order (not all registered users)
+- `lastActive` is null when a user has no orders
+- Trends use day-granularity bucketing based on order `createdAt`
+- Supported metrics are 'orders' (count) and 'revenue' (sum of totals); unsupported metrics throw
+
